messages.message: Hellllo! Does anyone have any experience using/implementing Amplitude? Or, just an interest in it? :slightly_smiling_face: I'm looking for another frontend engineer to join my IBHack team!

CJ briefly looked into using faro-core (https://github.com/grafana/faro-web-sdk/tree/main/packages/core) and faro-web-sdk (https://github.com/grafana/faro-web-sdk/tree/main/packages/web-sdk) to send frontend logs/errors to grafana, but Amplitude might be nice on the multi-tenant environment!

@danny.lan previously mentioned being interested in frontend observability too
